Shrimp cocktail is often served in a glass or a small bowl, beautifully arranged to showcase the shrimp. The shrimp are typically placed around the rim of the glass or bowl, creating an attractive presentation. This arrangement allows easy access to the shrimp and also makes for an eye-catching display.

